Class ThreadPool

java.lang.Object
  gov.nih.nlm.meme.server.ThreadPool
All Implemented Interfaces:
Initializable
public class ThreadPool
extends Object
implements Initializable

Represents a pool of threads. To use this class you must create a thread pool object and initialize passing an instance of a server context. For example,

   ThreadPool tp = new ThreadPool();
